- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and document embeddings. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also likely as the paper discusses nearest neighbor mining of parallel data. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper explores different document-level representations and models. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper uses neural networks for document encoding. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still a possibility as the paper discusses the effectiveness of different models on noisy data, which could be relevant to image processing.
